{"sectionId":743,"sectionIdLiteral":"743","humanId":"lesson-321","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"Father, my freedom is in You alone.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 321"},"annotation":"W-321","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-321\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"743#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>I did not understand what made me free, nor what my freedom is, nor where to look to find it.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Father, I have searched in vain until I heard Your Voice directing me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Now I would guide myself no more.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>For I have neither made nor understood the way to find my freedom.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>But I trust in You.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>You Who endowed me with my freedom as Your holy Son will not be lost to me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Your Voice directs me, and the way to You is opening and clear to me at last.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>Father, my freedom is in You alone.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#1:9\"><span class=\"snr\">9</span>Father, it is my will that I return.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"743#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Today we answer for the world, which will be freed along with us.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>How glad are we to find our freedom through the certain way our Father has established.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"743#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And how sure is all the world‚Äôs salvation, when we learn our freedom can be found in God alone.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"I did not understand what made me free, nor what my freedom is, nor where to look to find it. Father, I have searched in vain until I heard Your Voice directing me. Now I would guide myself no more.","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 321: Father, my freedom is in You alone | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†321 ‚ÄúFather, my freedom is in You alone‚Äù: I did not understand what made me free, nor what my freedom is, nor where to‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"11. What Is Creation?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":742,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-creation"]}},{"label":"Lesson 321","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":743,"slugs":["lesson-321","father-my-freedom-is-in-you-alone"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"11. What Is Creation?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":742,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-creation"]}},{"label":"Lesson 321","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":743,"slugs":["lesson-321","father-my-freedom-is-in-you-alone"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"11. What Is Creation?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":742,"slugs":["work